@startuml
title Book Seats - Sequence Diagram

actor User
boundary UI as "Web UI (HTML/CSS)"
control JS as "script.js"
database LS as "localStorage"

User -> UI: Open index.html
User -> UI: Click "Book Tickets"
UI -> User: Show page2.html

User -> UI: Click available seat
UI -> JS: toggleSeat(seatId)
JS -> UI: Update status + summary

User -> UI: Click "Confirm Booking"
UI -> JS: build bookingData(team,seats)
JS -> LS: setItem("bookingData", data)
JS -> UI: redirect confirm.html

User -> UI: Click "Finish Booking"
UI -> LS: move bookingData -> lastBooking
UI -> User: redirect thanks.html

@enduml